    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1R"/>
            <p>
                <placeName>Charleston</placeName>
                <date>3<hi rend="sup">rd</hi> Nov. 1852</date>
            </p>
            <p>
                <addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Dear Friend</p>
            <p rend="indent(4)">By this days mail I have<lb/> forwarded you a charity sermon
                delivered by the<lb/>
                <persName>Revd. Solomon Jacobs</persName> in behalf of the sick and<lb/> indigent.
                $300 were collected on that occasion.<lb/> I beg as a favor that you will notice
                the<lb/> sermon in the <date>Novr</date> No of the Occident.<lb/> So far our
                congregation are very much pleased<lb/> with him particularly his discourses,
                which<lb/> are forcible, persuasive and eloquent.__</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">He delivered one on last <date>sabbath</date> on “Free<lb/>
                Agency„—which I deemed his best, = It was<lb/> philosophical &amp; original, logical
                yet simple<lb/> enough for the most limited mind to comprehend.—<lb/> The Reformers
                are much pleased with him as<lb/> many of them are regular attendants each
                    <date>sabbath</date>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">We hope to effect a reunion.= The only<lb/> barrier is
                    <persName>Poznanski </persName> , <persName>Jacobs</persName> &amp; a few
                others—<lb/>but circumstances will compel them to yield<lb/> in time.</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Excuse haste I am very busy</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">Yours truly</p>
            <p rend="indent(4)">
                <persName role="author">Nathl Se<add>?</add></persName>
            </p>
            <p><persName>Mrs L.</persName> and all your friends</p>
            <p>d<add>?</add> their kindest regards.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">We have had a severe &amp; sickly season, and many</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">deaths worry our people—</p>
            <pb n="2V"/>
            <p rend="indent(4)">
                <addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(5)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(6)">
                <placeName>Pen</placeName>
            </p>
        </body>
